## 4) Legal and compliance notes (must-do)

- Respect each provider's Terms of Service and attribution rules.
- Add per-source usage throttling and retry policies.
- Store license metadata per record (`source`, `license`, `redistribution_allowed`).
- Separate personal data handling behind RBAC + audit logging.
- Use jurisdiction-specific legal review before enabling identity/background integrations.

